001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 279,
011    displayName = "Basal Delivery",
012    internalName = "LID_BASAL_DELIVERY",
013    usedByTidepool = true
014)
015public class BasalDeliveryHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
016    
017    private int commandedRateSource;
018    private int commandedRate;
019    private int profileBasalRate;
020    private int algorithmRate;
021    private int tempRate;
022    
023    public BasalDeliveryHistoryLog() {}
024    public BasalDeliveryHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int commandedRateSource, int commandedRate, int profileBasalRate, int algorithmRate, int tempRate) {
025        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
026        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, commandedRateSource, commandedRate, profileBasalRate, algorithmRate, tempRate);
027        this.commandedRateSource = commandedRateSource;
028        this.commandedRate = commandedRate;
029        this.profileBasalRate = profileBasalRate;
030        this.algorithmRate = algorithmRate;
031        this.tempRate = tempRate;
032        
033    }
034
035    public BasalDeliveryHistoryLog(int commandedRateSource, int commandedRate, int profileBasalRate, int algorithmRate, int tempRate) {
036        this(0, 0, commandedRateSource, commandedRate, profileBasalRate, algorithmRate, tempRate);
037    }
038
039    public int typeId() {
040        return 279;
041    }
042
043    /**
044     * <table border="1">
045     * <caption>Parsed fields for BasalDeliveryHistoryLog:</caption>
046     * <tr><td><code>commandedRateSource</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
047     * <tr><td><code>commandedRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
048     * <tr><td><code>profileBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
049     * <tr><td><code>algorithmRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>tempRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 20)</code></td></tr>
051     * </table>
052     */
053    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
054        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
055        this.cargo = raw;
056        parseBase(raw);
057        this.commandedRateSource = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
058        this.commandedRate = Bytes.readShort(raw, 14);
059        this.profileBasalRate = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
060        this.algorithmRate = Bytes.readShort(raw, 18);
061        this.tempRate = Bytes.readShort(raw, 20);
062        
063    }
064
065    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int commandedRateSource, int commandedRate, int profileBasalRate, int algorithmRate, int tempRate) {
066        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
067            new byte[]{23, 0}, // (byte) 279
068            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
069            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
070            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(commandedRateSource), 
071            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(commandedRate), 
072            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(profileBasalRate), 
073            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(algorithmRate), 
074            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(tempRate)));
075    }
076    public int getCommandedRateSource() {
077        return commandedRateSource;
078    }
079    public int getCommandedRate() {
080        return commandedRate;
081    }
082    public int getProfileBasalRate() {
083        return profileBasalRate;
084    }
085    public int getAlgorithmRate() {
086        return algorithmRate;
087    }
088    public int getTempRate() {
089        return tempRate;
090    }
091    
092}
